data.description: Light and airy 3 bedrooms, 2 bath single-family home.  4th bedroom can be used as a bonus/family room. Living room w/ wood-burning fireplace. New flooring, new carpets, new interior paint, new roof, newer furnace. Main Bath recently remodeled. The kitchen has a sliding glass door that leads onto the deck from there you can entertain or just admire the peaceful setting on the deck with panoramic views that include Mt. Rainer. Oversized 2 car attached garage with alley access. Close to everything.
